      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
