      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found! It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept since day one, so it still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for like family, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! \u2728",
